import React, { Component } from "react";
import styled, { css } from "styled-components";

function Calculator(props) {
  return (
    <>
      <Header>
        <MillionairMakerStackStack>
          <MillionairMakerStack>
            <MillionairMaker>Millionair Maker</MillionairMaker>
            <InitialDeposit placeholder="$0"></InitialDeposit>
            <InitialDeposit1 placeholder="$0"></InitialDeposit1>
          </MillionairMakerStack>
          <Label>Starting Cash</Label>
        </MillionairMakerStackStack>
      </Header>
      <EarlyTitle>Early Life savings phase</EarlyTitle>
      <EarlyLife></EarlyLife>
      <BallerLifeTitle>Baller Life savings phase</BallerLifeTitle>
      <BallerLifeStack>
        <BallerLife></BallerLife>
        <Worth>
          <HowRichAmI>How rich am I?</HowRichAmI>
          <RichLabelRow>
            <RichLabel>Total savings:</RichLabel>
            <RichLabel1>$0</RichLabel1>
          </RichLabelRow>
        </Worth>
      </BallerLifeStack>
    </>
  );
}
